						<div class="postbody">I set _IRQ at the same time the frame IRQ flag is set. The IRQ handler is ran, unless the CPU was just fetching a new opcode. So practically, a delay of one instruction may sometimes happen, in the same way when enabling NMIs in the middle of vblank before reading $2002.</div>

